#

# How to Add Supporting Browser's list in a Project

- Inside your Package.json
  "browserList": [
  "last 2 Chrome versions",
  "last 2 Firefox versions"
  ]

- To specify the versions we can check the link

* url -> browserlist.dev

- The above configuration means the code will run defenetly on the given version's and might not for other versions
